            I know that the hon. Gentleman has walked extensively in Cornwall. He will be glad to know that, as from 9 am today, virtually all footpaths in the county are open.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0371P0_20010703_WH_40'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-paddy-tipping' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
